Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting Jimbei again at the Sea Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy learns about the Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with Nami, Sanji, Chopper,\N Franky and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that we're like \Nthose stupid Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to her hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:30.91,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Death of the Hero! \NA Shocking Truth of Tiger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:38.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally got an Eternal \NPose to Koala's hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:38.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}12 YEARS AGO - THE GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyu! Koala, you can go back to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my eyes. \NYou've changed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:55.31,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}KOALA (THE FORMER SLAVE GIRL)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a girl now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't normally wear these...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We bought them for you\N but you don't like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your hair cut, too. \NYour mother will be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyu! You need to stop working \Nwhen you don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not Marie Jois!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.80,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:31.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE SHIP'S DOCTOR OF THE SUN PIRATES\NALADDIN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Trauma can't be healed that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand her very\N well, Brother Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were a slave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't you rather kill her right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a human just like \Nthe one who owned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us the truth. \NWhat did your mother tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents looked down \Non Fish-Men, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how human society is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think that they're \Nthe best race in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their children are spoiled \Nby watching their example.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't stop until somebody destroys them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you guys have seen it enough \Nwhile we were sailing these past 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their disrespectful \Ncontemptuous look when they see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I would've done \Nto them if the Boss wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was only a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The others didn't look like that.\N--Brother Jimbei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everytime I see them, \Nthey all look terrified to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because we're pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so afraid of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't know you folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know someone,\N you naturally fear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only known the bad sort of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything about humans yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So getting to know someone\N would change something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyu. Hey, Koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess which hand it's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyu. Get it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Koala was fitting in so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when we arrived at Foolshout\N Island - where she came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:17.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE GRAND LINE - FOOLSHOUT ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Koala, get off of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your home island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where is your home village?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll walk you to the entrance to the village.\N--Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Koala! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl even \Nthough you're a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell everybody in the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that there are so many good Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll grow up into a \Nmean-spirited human like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jimbei. \NYou've changed a lot in last 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it. What's the point in her \Ntelling people that Fish-Men are nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Otohime's speeches,\N her voice will just ring hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Your daughter is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm so glad!\N--Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! She came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koala? Koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the captain of the Sun Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bad man, isn't he?\N Because he's a Fish-Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been painful\N and hard being a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mom, not everybody was \Nlike the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Fish-Men were all terrible \Nbut there were so many nice Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're only a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I know it because I was with Uncle \NTiger and the others all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would think so too \Nif you'd lived with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for keeping your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget you - Uncle Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hachi-san,\N Aladdin-san and all of the Sun Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that when you grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,humans and Fish-Men will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rear Admiral Strawberry \Nfrom the Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone on this island \Ninformed us of your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elders of this village knew there\N might be trouble if we stopped you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they approved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the condition that we wouldn't repossess\N the girl who is the rightful property
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger, captain of the Sun Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are charged on two counts.\N I'm sure you know this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assault and evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I heard gunshots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the direction Boss headed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Navy! We're surrounded-choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat was a ploy to lure us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Big Brother and all \Nof us took it like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! That's what humans do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss Tai is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle this? We \Ngotta go save the Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Brother Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to bring Big Brother back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san, this is not good!\N The ship is gonna be wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, get off of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hijack one of the Navy ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been shot so many times!\N Why is he still standing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you! \NI won't forgive you, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I heard something.\N Did you hear anything, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rear Admiral-dono! The Sun Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're responsible for all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I've done is for justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and to destroy the Sun Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! I'd like to see you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to rescue Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and flee to sea with a Navy\N ship that Arlong stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean that you don't\N want a transfusion? Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost too much blood! \NYou're gonna die if you don't get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Boss' blood type is rare! No one \Nin our crew has the same blood type!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood stock on this Navy ship must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. But humans \Nand we share the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can use human blood to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than live with their blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their blood is filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They never stop disrespecting us Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna owe them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need mercy from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna give in to humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Was there something...\N between you and the humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't wanna tell you this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my last trip, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long trip, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see during your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after I set off on my trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I was caught.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent several years in Marie Jois.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I saw there was the insanity of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fled for my life but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't just forget about\N all those slaves that I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did things the way I wanted and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I interfered with Queen \NOtohime as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wants peace, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only people who can make\N a difference on that island...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are children of the next generation\N like Koala who aren't prejudiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people \Non the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the tragedy we endured \Nnor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many humans \Nwho are compassionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's funny - the dying leave \Nonly their resentment behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though I know \Nthat there are kind humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a devil inside of me that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...clouding my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My whole body rejects their blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...accept humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Don't say such a \Nthing and live! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! No matter what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the greatest benefactor to \Nall the slaves who were freed by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hero to all Fish-Men, \Nwho accomplished such a great feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to step further. You can't \Nprotect anybody with that punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is nobody else \Nwho wants to challenge me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the leader of the \NFish-Man District from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm your brother now,\N leave everything up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep my men safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tigers death sent \Nripples far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Fish-Men and humans coexist, \Nor must they remain separate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Fish-Men waver, \NArlong's hatred of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Jimbei's desire to preserve \NOtohime and Tiger's ideals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will bring their convictions into conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Sun Pirates Split! Jimbei vs Arlong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
